{"tid":1007880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"草地亂倫繼母 …大哥陰莖慘遭同父異母弟「扯爆」亡","createTime":"2019-02-04T05:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T08:11:55.000Z","uid":205996,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"230ca0ae18691e002b934dd74973cc9f47c750cc","tid":1007880,"uid":205996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/06/21/946363-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F946363-XXL.jpg&h=041741ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男下體遭扯爆亡<br />\n<br />\n辛巴威34歲的男子夏含巴（Siyahamba Mukukuzi），日前忍不住在草地上大搞自己的繼母，結果被兩名同父異母的弟弟撞見，憤怒的弟弟們當場扯爆夏含巴的陰莖，最後夏含巴因失血過多慘死。<br />\n<br />\n根據《每日郵報》報導，這兩名扯爆哥哥陰莖的男子，分別是24歲的哈德來福（Hardlife Chimoko Sithole）及20歲的羅伊德（Lloyd Mukukuzi）。哈德來福與羅伊德應訊時表示，當時目睹哥哥夏含巴與母親茱麗葉特（Juliet Mukeketsi）發生親密關係後，只拿出皮帶對夏含巴抽打，並未拉扯他的陰莖。<br />\n<br />\n不過，茱麗葉特則表示，她並沒有和繼子夏含巴發生「亂倫」。哈德來福與羅伊德被捕後，都被判15年有期徒刑。這則新聞曝光後引發網友熱議，有人就說，「媽媽還裝傻」、「沒想到會死在自己弟弟的鷹爪手」，也有人說，「陰莖充血狀態才扯得下來吧？」"},{"pid":"733606475eb2f79a6e6b6ab2bd41ca59894b0338","tid":1007880,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"old news?"},{"pid":"dcc4c67a8f5749602e243f808614803f27d61fd0","tid":1007880,"uid":126609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:43:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2255e475764468140131976d7b1b876e3d7379ec","tid":1007880,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:43:38.000Z","msg":"召喚大王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ef7bf36b5e18c0912cb9b2db2ffcc4da37638e","tid":1007880,"uid":10890,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T06:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jfvNwSZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjfvNwSZ.png&h=0c3af656&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2190644c84f28de8b157cd30922560e7f8cc2f23",